OL,3,CLondon mayor to invest #100m in new
OL,4,Chomes through 'Singapore-style'
OL,5,Cdevelopment
OL,7,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan has
OL,8,Fannounced a #100 million investment in
OL,9,Fa new homes scheme, inspired by
OL,10,FSingapore's housing approach.
OL,12,FCity Hall will join the Silvertown
OL,13,FPartnership and support the delivery
OL,14,Fof 7,000 new homes in the Royal Docks
OL,15,Fin east London.
OL,17,FAbout 1,000 of the new homes are
OL,18,Fexpected to be under construction by
OL,19,F2028.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
