PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781812086
OL,3,CLondon mayor to invest #100m in new
OL,4,Chomes through 'Singapore-style'
OL,5,Cdevelopment
OL,7,FThe investment is part of a new City
OL,8,FHall Developer scheme modelled on
OL,9,FSingapore's approach to housing
OL,10,Fdevelopment in which the state plays a
OL,11,Fcentral role by building 80% of homes
OL,12,Fand owning most of the land.
OL,14,FSir Sadiq said he hoped the initiative
OL,15,Fwould allow City Hall to become an
OL,16,Factive developer in more sites across
OL,17,Fthe capital, to help maximise
OL,18,Faffordable housing delivery.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
