PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781812086
OL,3,CLondon mayor to invest #100m in new
OL,4,Chomes through 'Singapore-style'
OL,5,Cdevelopment
OL,7,FThe announcement was made during the
OL,8,Fmayor's trade mission to Singapore and
OL,9,FJapan, where he is promoting London as
OL,10,Fa leading global destination for
OL,11,Finvestment.
OL,13,FSir Sadiq said: "I am delighted to be
OL,14,Flaunching our groundbreaking
OL,15,F'Singapore-style' housing development
OL,16,Farm for the capital today.
OL,26,@uD@QOU
