PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781812086
OL,3,CLondon mayor to invest #100m in new
OL,4,Chomes through 'Singapore-style'
OL,5,Cdevelopment
OL,7,F"I'm proud to be investing #100
OL,8,Fmillion, one of the largest
OL,9,Finvestments made by any mayor of
OL,10,FLondon, to help build and deliver
OL,11,Fthousands of new, high-quality and
OL,12,Faffordable homes at Silvertown.
OL,14,F"This is a new era for housebuilding
OL,15,Fin London, with City Hall investing
OL,16,Fdirectly in new homes, unblocking
OL,17,Fstalled sites and speeding up
OL,18,Fdevelopment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@MO]
