CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781812086
OL,3,CLondon mayor to invest #100m in new
OL,4,Chomes through 'Singapore-style'
OL,5,Cdevelopment
OL,7,FThe mayor said of the new investment:
OL,8,F"It builds on our record investment of
OL,9,Fnearly #12 billion through my
OL,10,Faffordable homes programme to deliver
OL,11,Fsocial and affordable housing across
OL,12,FLondon and our package of pro-housing
OL,13,Femergency measures with government to
OL,14,Fturbo-boost the delivery of new homes
OL,15,Fin the capital."
